004import java.time.ZonedDateTime;
005import java.util.List;
006
007import javax.validation.Valid;
008import javax.validation.constraints.NotNull;

010import com.commercetools.api.models.cart.*;

020public interface OrderLike<T extends OrderLike<T>> {

024    @NotNull

026
027    @NotNull
028    public ZonedDateTime getCreatedAt();
029
030    @NotNull

032
033    @Valid

036    @Valid

038
039    public String getCustomerId();
040
041    public String getCustomerEmail();
042
043    public String getAnonymousId();
044
045    @Valid

047
048    @NotNull

051

054    public List<CustomLineItem> getCustomLineItems();
055
056    @NotNull
057    @Valid
058    public TypedMoney getTotalPrice();
059
060    @Valid

063    @Valid
064    public Address getShippingAddress();
065
066    @Valid

068
069    public InventoryMode getInventoryMode();

071    @NotNull

073

076

079
080    @Valid

082
083    public String getCountry();
084
085    @Valid
086    public ShippingInfo getShippingInfo();
087
088    @Valid
089    public List<DiscountCodeInfo> getDiscountCodes();
090
091    @Valid
092    public CustomFields getCustom();
093
094    @Valid
095    public PaymentInfo getPaymentInfo();
096
097    public String getLocale();
098
099    @NotNull
100    @Valid
101    public List<CartDiscountReference> getRefusedGifts();
102
103    @NotNull
104    public CartOrigin getOrigin();
105
106    @Valid
107    public ShippingRateInput getShippingRateInput();

109    @Valid
110    public List<Address> getItemShippingAddresses();
